    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "so it's basically like these waste products are just actively interfering with everything in the muscle tissue? feels a bit like there's some kind of chaotic disruption happening inside the cells. is there a way to explain that disruption more simply? like if you had to describe the way those molecules act to mess with the cell's normal work, how would that look?",
